    Tracking¶

    Equations of motion:

    $\frac{dz}{dt} = \frac{pc}{\sqrt{(pc)^2 + m^2 c^4)}} c$

    $\frac{dp}{dt} = q E_z $

    $E_z = \Re f(z) \exp(-i \omega t) $

    Copied!
